metadata.name: NatatliaK
metadata.description:
Natalia and I reunited after few years in LA for a shoot in the magical El Matador beach. It was a very windy day, and the biggest challenge was playing with the wind, transforming it from an enemy to an ally! Adding waves and movements to fabrics and hair, was actually crucial in increasing that sense of freedom and harmony with nature that we wanted to inspire and communicate.

This as everyone of the future NFT will be bundled with a printed copy (17x22) that will be shipped to the original buyer
